        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Prodapt has a singular focus on the Connectedness vertical. We partner with the leading creators of our hyper-connected world. Prodapt’s customers range from telecom operators, digital / multi-service providers (D/MSPs), technology and digital platform companies in the business of connectedness. Prodapt builds, integrates, and operates solutions enabling next-generation technologies and innovations. Prodapt services global leaders including AT&T, Verizon, CenturyLink, Adtran, Vodafone, Liberty Global, Windstream, Virgin Media, Rogers, Deutsche Telekom among many others. Prodapt’s customers today help more than a billion people and five billion devices stay connected.Employing over 3500+ people, Prodapt has offices in the North America, Europe, Latam, India, and Africa. We are part of the 120-year-old business conglomerate, The Jhaver Group, which employs over 22,000 people across 64+ locations globally.</p>
